{"id":2938,"date":"2022-05-01T12:50:25","date_gmt":"2022-05-01T09:50:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/?p=2938"},"modified":"2022-05-01T12:50:25","modified_gmt":"2022-05-01T09:50:25","slug":"top-nft-tools-for-tracking-nft-projects","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/top-nft-tools-for-tracking-nft-projects\/","title":{"rendered":"Top NFT Tools for Tracking NFT Projects"},"content":{"rendered":"<p> <br \/>\n<\/p>\n<div itemprop=\"mainEntityOfPage\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">NFTs are becoming increasingly popular by radically transforming the world of digital ownership, with no sign of slowing down anytime soon. New NFT projects are introduced every day, and it is vital for those who have invested in NFTs or are interested in investing in NFTs to keep track of the most popular NFT initiatives in order to make sensible investments.<br \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manually tracking NFT projects is a time-consuming process, and to help you solve this problem, below are some analytical tools for tracking trending NFT projects.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><b>BitDegree<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/bitdegree_org\">BitDegree<\/a> can be used to discover and analyze various NFT collections available on the market. At the time of writing, BitDegree is currently tracking 357 different NFT collections from three protocols, scattered across 58 different NFT marketplaces.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>With BitDegree, you can search for accessible NFT collections and examine their data for further information. Additionally, you can use a variety of indicators on the platform to improve the analysis of any NFT. BitDegree allows you to create your portfolio and keep track of all of your favourite NFTs in one place.<\/p>\n<p>The best part about this tool is that it tracks everything so you can make the right judgments at the right time. BitDegree also gives you a breakdown of the most popular NFT collections. As a result, you\u2019ll be well-informed on which NFTs are currently gaining traction in the market.<\/p>\n<h4><b>Moby<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/mobyinsights\">Moby<\/a> is not widely used, it is a good NFT tracking tool, as it provides the most up-to-date NFT statistics and feeds, and also helps users to track their holdings. Moby is limited unless upgraded to a Pro version.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Upgrading to the Pro edition of Moby opens accessibility to all data visualizations, such as historical collecting data, real-time feeds, NFT signals, and more, which will aid investors in undertaking more in-depth research. Moby\u2019s ranking system for NFTs can help you locate the best contracts and decide which ones to invest in.<\/p>\n<h4><b>Crypto.com<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another tracking tool is <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/cryptocom\">Crypto.com<\/a>, which can supply you with all of the necessary information about the top NFT collections in the NFT market. You can also get data depending on the price and volume of any NFT.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>When you go to the official website, you\u2019ll see a list of the top NFT collections and information on their total assets, collection worth, floor price, volume, and sales. On Crypto.com, you can also look for upcoming NFT collections to see if there are any interesting projects to invest in. Visitors can examine these NFT collections and learn about their asset value, drop date, minting price, etc.<\/p>\n<h4><b>Rarity.tools<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/raritytools\">Rarity.tools<\/a> is an easy-to-use tool that gives you thorough information and assists you in finding specific information about NFT collections. The rarity of an NFT is an important factor to consider when purchasing it. The best NFTs, which have sold for millions of dollars, are exceedingly uncommon (rare) and sought after by all collectors.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>This is one of the reasons their price is so high (but not the only reason). Rarity.tools is an excellent tool for exploring and tracking the NFT universe. On rarity.tools, you may sort all the NFTs by their collections, average price, and even volume in ETH.<\/p>\n<h4><b>Icy.tools<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The first thing you\u2019ll notice when you open <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/icy_tools\">Icy.tools<\/a> is the \u2018Trending Collections,\u2019 which displays some of the most popular NFTs from the previous day. An innovative feature of icy.tools is the \u201cleaderboard\u201d containing all relevant information about NFTs, such as the floor price, volume, sales, and average price. It has a user-friendly interface, making NFT analysis simple even for beginners.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>You may also find the wallet addresses of some of the marketplace\u2019s top buyers and sellers if you look through the \u2018Discover Tab\u2019. Upgrading to the premium subscription, you will have access to detailed information pages for each NFT collection which features the history and price charts for each NFT.<\/p>\n<h4><b>NFT Drops Calendar<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/NftDropsCal\">NFT Drops Calendar<\/a> is a tool that keeps track of all the future drops. It will not only keep you up to date on all upcoming NFT releases, but it will also notify you about freebies, events, and sales involving NFTs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With the use of various search tags, you may also search for any specific NFT collection on this platform. Furthermore, the sorting option allows you to organize all of the NFTs by various criteria such as minting date, price, volume, and more. Users of the NFT Drops Calendar can also submit their own NFTs to be listed for sale on the site. When it comes to NFTs, it\u2019s essentially a one-stop-shop.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><b>DappRadar<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/DappRadar\">DappRadar<\/a> has been a go-to site for tracking the sales data of NFT collections for a long time. DappRadar has a portfolio tracker to provide users with a simple way to monitor Ethereum wallets in real-time.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you\u2019re searching for a tool to help you keep track of your portfolios and also a tool that displays the most popular NFTs in the market depending on various timeframes, DappRadar is an excellent option. Aside from that, you can see the volume, traders, and sales of any NFT collection right now. Not only this, but DappRadar also allows you to keep track of the most popular NFT collections and track real-time sales.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><b>Upcoming NFT<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another helpful tool for staying up to date on anticipated NFT drops is <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/upcomingNFT_art\">Upcoming NFT<\/a>. This platform will inform you of impending NFT projects, events, drops, auctions, or giveaways. You can sort the NFT projects by popularity, time of addition, or even by upcoming projects.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To get more exposure, you can also submit your NFT to Upcoming NFT if you\u2019re thinking about starting your own NFT project. Upcoming NFT will allow you to obtain attention and find a prospective buyer for your digital artwork. The Upcoming NFT live feed tool allows investors to study the trending NFTs that are being minted on the blockchain in real-time and gain additional insight into them.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upcoming NFT can also assist you in promoting your NFT projects. You can put yourself in the spotlight to get better deals later on through promotions even before your project goes live. You can also get real-time data and insights for all scheduled NFT events on this platform.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you\u2019re interested in investing in the NFT industry, you\u2019ll want to keep track of upcoming NFT launches. Numerous NFT tracking tools are available to ensure that you never miss out on any popular or trending NFTs on the market.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nftplazas\/\">Follow us on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n<p><small><em>*All investment\/financial opinions expressed by NFT Plazas are from the personal research and experience of our site moderators and are intended as educational material only. Individuals are required to fully research any product prior to making any kind of investment.<\/em><\/small><\/p>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"author\">\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-tab\">\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-gravatar\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-desc\">\n<div itemprop=\"description\">\n<p>Technical writer, an enthusiast for everything blockchai